      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-4 mb-6">How to How to Turn Your Healthcare Site Into a Mobile App</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Learn how to convert your healthcare website into a mobile app, to boost engagement and retention, and keep up with modern user habits, and why MobiLoud is the best option for healthcare mobile app development.</p>
